```{r}
rr_a = ggarrange(r1, r3, r2, r4,common.legend=T,legend="right",ncol = 2,nrow=2)


ggpubr::annotate_figure(rr_a,top="Fitted Values (Logged) v/s BMI and Age Categories",left="Age Categories",bottom="BMI Categories")
```


